<h3><a class="toc-backref" href="#id27">1.4.4.4. Contour Plots</a><a class="headerlink" href="#contour-plots" title="Permalink to this headline">¶</a></h3>
<a class="reference external image-reference" href="auto_examples/plot_contour_ex.html"><img alt="../../_images/plot_contour_ex_1.png" class="align-right" src="../../_images/plot_contour_ex_1.png" style="width: 280.0px; height: 210.0px;" /></a>
